This mod was developed with great care and dedication for our [url=https://discord.gg/zqJUS7WvMv]Última Esperança[/url] community—thank you for all your support!—and I believe it’s a mod that will help many other communities, which is why I’m making it public for the entire Project Zomboid community.  

If you enjoyed the mod and would like to support my work, feel free to contact me for more information on how to contribute. Your support helps me continue developing new things for the game!  

Feedback and suggestions are extremely welcome. Leave your rating and comments to help improve the mod!  

